                <p>Test your system regularly to ensure all components are working correctly and that you can access live feeds and recorded footage as expected. Have a plan for system failures, including backup monitoring methods and emergency contacts. Regular testing and maintenance help ensure your security system provides reliable protection when you need it most.</p>
