                <p>Backup and recovery procedures help ensure that you can restore your voice control system in case of device failure or data loss. Regularly backup device configurations, custom routines, and important settings. Test your backup and recovery procedures to ensure they work correctly, and consider using cloud backup services for critical data.</p>
                
