                <p>Warranty and support services can provide valuable assistance with device issues and maintenance needs. Understand the warranty coverage for your smart home devices and keep records of warranty information. Contact manufacturer support for issues covered under warranty, and consider extended warranty or support plans for critical devices.</p>
                
